info.profile: Jinshan Pan is a Professor at the Nanjing University of Science and Technology. He got the Ph.D. degree from School of Mathematical Sciences, Dalian University of Technology in 2017. Before that, he was a joint-training Ph.D. student in School of Mathematical Sciences, Dalian University of Technology and Electrical Engineering and Computer Science, University of California at Merced, directed by Profs. Zhixun Su and Ming-Hsuan Yang. He was a visiting Ph.D. student in Visual Computing Group at Harvard University, working with Prof. Hanspeter Pfister and Dr. Deqing Sun in 2015
